Jim Varney -- Ernest -- was someone who brought smiles to our faces nearly twenty years ago and still does to this day -- you couldn't ask for a better experience and what is in fact a fairly priced piece of nostalgia, know what I mean, Vern?  Thanks Jim!
good value
The dvd pack that I received was 100% as described. Still packaged as expected. This was NOT a pirated copy. I love it!

When compared to the programs children watch today, children of the 80's and 90's were exposed to a lot more than today.  As an adult watching these films is kinda corney, but they do take me back to my childhood.  Nothing great or memorable, just fun to recall Ernest and his goofy antics.
These were my sons favorite growing up.  He would laugh so hard.  He now has a 9 year old son, that I bought these for.  He laughs and watches them over and over.
timeless entertainment for the grandkids.
